---
title: Cheat's Eggplant Parmigiana with Avocado-Cucumber Salad
description: Yes, you can whip up an eggplant parmie at home – it’s not that hard! At least our version isn’t – with satisfying eggplant steaks that are lightly fried until golden then baked to get the signature cheesy tomato topping. Served with a fresh and hearty salad, this shows you can improve on the classics!
